StoredProcedureSqlServerv2k5.name: [GetO.cerWaiverAtachmentsForO.cerWaiver]
StoredProcedureSqlServerv2k5.body:
@O.cerWaiverID int AS
SELECT OFFICER_WAIVER_ATTACHMENT_ID, OFFICER_WAIVER_ID, NAME, UPLOAD_DATE, UPLOADED_BY FROM [dbo].[OFFICER_WAIVER_ATTACHMENT] WITH (NOLOCK) WHERE OFFICER_WAIVER_ID = @O.cerWaiverID ORDER BY UPLOAD_DATE DESC
